---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Sales Analysis">
    <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-20 md:py-40">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-center text-cyan-400">Sales Analysis</h1>
        <section class="mb-8 bg-white dark:bg-slate-600 rounded-lg shadow p-6">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2 text-cyan-400">Project Overview</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-white">
                This project focuses on sales data analysis using data science techniques. The goal is to extract valuable insights from historical sales data to support business decision-making.
            </p>
        </section>
        <section class="mb-8 bg-white dark:bg-slate-600 rounded-lg shadow p-6">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2 text-cyan-400">Objectives</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 dark:text-white space-y-1">
                <li>Identify sales trends and seasonality.</li>
                <li>Detect top-performing products and regions.</li>
                <li>Forecast future sales using predictive models.</li>
                <li>Provide actionable recommendations for business growth.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
        <section class="mb-8 bg-white dark:bg-slate-600 rounded-lg shadow p-6">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2 text-cyan-400">Technologies Used</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 dark:text-white space-y-1">
                <li>Python (Pandas, NumPy, Matplotlib, Scikit-learn)</li>
                <li>Jupyter Notebook</li>
                <li>SQL for data extraction</li>
                <li>Power BI for visualization</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
        <section class="mb-8 bg-white dark:bg-slate-600 rounded-lg shadow p-6">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2 text-cyan-400">Key Findings</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 dark:text-white space-y-1">
                <li>Seasonal peaks in sales during Q4.</li>
                <li>Product X and Y are the most profitable.</li>
                <li>Region North consistently outperforms others.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
        <section class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-600 rounded-lg shadow p-6">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2 text-cyan-400">Conclusion</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-white">
                The analysis provided actionable insights that helped optimize inventory, improve marketing strategies, and increase overall sales performance.
            </p>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>